</ul>
<p>Our client offer you a challenging position in an exciting, high-profile role. This is an opportunity to join a company where your creativity and expertise will be appreciated. This person will be instrumental in providing our client with a data environment that can grow with their business. With buy-in from senior management, you will have all the tools you need to be successful in this role.</p><img src="https://counter.adcourier.com/SkxDUy44NjM3Ni4xMTEzMEBzdGhyZWVubC5hcGxpdHJhay5jb20.gif">', 'HuxleyIT', NULL, 'Amsterdam', '2020-09-15 10:57:12.460835', 'competitive', 'Data Engineering Lead', 'HA-33558406', 'https://www.huxley.com/nl-nl/job/kyc/HA-33558406');
