INSERT INTO public.vacancy VALUES ('06b0b49f-26ad-40ec-a3c9-bbf23a0c012e', 'IT Chapter Lead Solliciteer Solliciteer op de website van de werkgever Premium 30+ dagen geleden ING IT Chapter Lead - Front End Platforms ING is transforming rapidly towards a top-notch IT company with a Top Engineering culture, incorporating FinTech start-up mentality and financial innovation. We are end-to-end agile, work in multidisciplinary teams and use cutting edge technology. This enables us to offer our customers the best possible services and respond to rapidly changing customer demands. We are looking for an energetic IT Chapter Lead with a passion for combining thought and action. You serve as an example and show that you are a true ambassador for the Agile way of working and the ING Orange culture. The customer perspective is your primary driver for working in a squad. What you‚Äôll do You will become a Front-end Platforms Chapter Lead within Omnichannel IT Domain. You are at the heart of both Java and JavaScript Technologies. With your engineers you will be working on Frontend platform, ING‚Äôs one-stop-shop for Front-end app development, which includes full spectrum of products and tools, enabling engineers to provide best user experience to our customers. You will help ING engineers around the globe by providing reusable components, development tools, continuous integration pipeline, as well as documentation, training materials and workshops. Our technology stack is built around webcomponents standards and Polymer ecosystem. For our microservices architecture we extensively use Java. Along with the IT Area Lead and your fellow IT Chapter Leads you determine the working methodology within your area of expertise, allocate specific knowledge/focus areas and set the standards. Above all, as IT Chapter Lead, you are a ‚Äúdoer‚Äù. Sixty percent of your time, you work as a squad member towards accomplishing a squad‚Äôs mission. You use your seniority to maximize team performance. Ho