INSERT INTO public.vacancy VALUES ('c70bb1ee-3499-4cf3-a073-67ae4b6b357d', 'Senior Software Engineer) - Cyber Security Artificial Intelligence (ING Internal Assignment or 6 months Fixed-Term Contract)- ING Labs Solliciteer Solliciteer op de website van de werkgever Premium 30+ dagen geleden ING Are you passionate about cyber security, big data and artificial intelligence? Are you up for the challenge to drive an initiative through our innovation framework? If this triggers your attention, you are in the right place. At the ING Labs, we are working on a new initiative that will combine these domains into cutting edge solutions. Your work environment ING‚Äôs purpose is to empower people in life and in business by increasing the pace of innovation to serve changing customer needs. ING Labs focus on thinking beyond traditional banking to develop new services to take to market. This specific initiative will focus on Cyber Security, AI and Big Data. You will be working in the ING Labs Amsterdam office in a very international and dynamic environment. Using ING‚Äôs customer led innovation process you will validate the key assumptions of the Cybersecurity proposition and business. A market to develop ING Labs funds disruptive ventures addressing multi-billion Euro market opportunities. Our initiative will support these ventures like Cobase and Yolt with a design process aimed at de-risking before going to market (using lean startup, design thinking & agile methodologies). Your role As a Senior Software Engineer, you will be the expert in your domain area and a key member of the team to support us in a new initiative starting from scratch. You are passionate and at your best working to solve very hard problems with a small highly skilled team. You want to work in a startup with the backing of a large innovative bank. Your curiosity and vision drive you to build what has never been built before. Your deliverables In the next 6 months, we are expected to bring this initiative t